{"type":"message","id":"c5b9c5e5","parentId":"275d8346","timestamp":"2026-03-31T21:32:49.314Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:04fada94-e9d7-467e-b0ad-86af5dac06e5 planner-自维护-3h] 执行 planner 独立自维护：\n1. cd ~/.openclaw/workspaces/feishu-planner\n2. 读取 HEARTBEAT.md、MEMORY.md 以及 memory/ 下最近 2 天的记录\n3. 整理并沉淀规划逻辑、任务拆解模式、飞书文档管理经验到 MEMORY.md\n4. 检查是否有长治理、待验收的规划任务，并在 MEMORY.md 中更新其状态\n5. 若无实质更新，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n注意：你当前的 workspace 是 ~/.openclaw/workspaces/feishu-planner，请只在此范围内活动。\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 2026 — 5:32 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-31 21:32 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774992769291}}
